Name: fibrosclerosis of breast
Definition: A non-proliferative fibrocystic change of the breast that contains scar tissue.
Output: non-proliferative fibrocystic change of the breast

Name: apocrine adenosis of breast
Definition: A non-proliferative fibrocystic change of the breast that is characterized by sclerosing adenosis with apocrine change.
Output: non-proliferative fibrocystic change of the breast
